&lt;p&gt;Part Time Scoopers at Van Leeuwen&#39;s scoop shops make $13.00 per hour + an average of an additional $10 per hour in tips!&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Tips are based on averages and subject to seasonal fluctuation. &lt;/em&gt;Our team members must have availability to work at least three shifts per week and be available to work past 12am.&lt;/p&gt;
